s, bonds, equity investments, financial close announcements (amount, lender/investor, status).\\n* **Notable contractors**: EPC, turbine supplier, or technology provider if named.\\n* **Source details**: title, publisher, URL, publication date.\\n* **Confidence level**: how strong the evidence is (official vs media vs rumor).\\nHuman: Spain\\nAI: \\nTool: [{\\\"query\\\":\\\"2026 construction start solar farm Spain permit approved 2025\\\",\\\"follow_up_questions\\\":null,\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Construction of a 200 MW solar farm in Spain's Andalusia region began in 2025, with operations starting in 2026. The project received necessary permits in 2025.\\\",\\\"images\\\":[],\\\"results\\\":[{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.eni.com/en-IT/media/press-release/2025/07/plenitude-begins-construction-new-200-mw-solar-park-spain.html\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Plenitude begins construction of a new 200 MW solar park ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"The Entrenúcleos project, located between Dos Hermanas and Coria del Río (Seville, Andalusia), is expected to begin operations in 2026 and generate more than\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.68798697,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.blackridgeresearch.com/blog/top-new-upcoming-europe-renewable-projects?srsltid=AfmBOorvoUleXSa0-yp5LX-e7J5-Oh8OQ6igcDMdbYc8M77yj1O6ARxf\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Top 10 New Upcoming Europe Renewable Projects in 2025\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"The Zaragoza & Teruel Solar Farm is being planned in the Zaragoza & Teruel provinces, Aragón region, Spain. It is being developed by Bruc Iberia\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.6188962,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://solarin.es/solar-incentives-in-spain-2025/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Solar Incentives in Spain 2025 - Solarin\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Deadline to apply: Applications are open until February 27, 2026. Where to apply: Through the official platform of the Generalitat Valenciana. Click here. 2\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.60917604,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"ht