-445-mwp-pv-plant-in-spain/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Q ENERGY builds 44.5 MWp PV plant in Spain\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"* About Q ENERGY **QENERGY Solutions SE****Q ENERGY Europe GmbH** **QENERGY Solutions SE****Q ENERGY Europe GmbH** # Q ENERGY builds 44.5 MWp PV plant in Spain Q ENERGY continues to expand its presence in the north of Spain and started construction of a new PV plant in the province of Teruel. **Q ENERGY Solutions SE** Corporate CommunicationsAmanda Baudry, Christian Köhn media@qenergy.eu Among other things, the quotations from management in this press release and Q ENERGY’s operations and business outlook, contain forward-looking statements. Except as required by law, Q ENERGY does not undertake any obligation to update or revise any forward-looking statements, whether as a result of new information, future events or otherwise.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.39985907,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://soltec.com/en/press-room/totalenergies-and-soltec-begin-the-construction-of-two-new-solar-parks-in-the-region-of-murcia/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"TotalEnergies and Soltec begin the construction of two new ...\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"The completion of the works is scheduled for October 2026. With more than 494,000 bifacial solar panels and solar tracking technology, the two\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.38525957,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://misolar.website/guide-installing-solar-panels-spain/\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Guide: Install Solar Panels in Spain (& get your bills to €0)\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Want to install solar panels in Spain? Find answers to all your questions about solar energy in Spain, solar panels, solar batteries,\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.21915402,\\\"raw_content\\\":null},{\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.investinspain.org/content/icex-invest/en/noticias-main/2025/statkraft2.html\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Statkraft to build first wind-solar project in Burgos Spain\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"Construction of the Cernégula project began in December 2023, and has involved an investment of 54 million euros and the creation of 140 jobs.\\\",\\\"score\\\":0.17749733,\\\"raw_content\\\":null}],\\\"response_time\\\":1.61,\\\"request_id\\\":\\\"eab99bcf-95c3-427b-963c-673ec4abbe5e\\\"}]\"],\"options\":{\"api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"GROQ_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"openai/gpt-oss-120b\",\"temperature\":0.7},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"tool_calls\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":139,\"promptTokens\":2118,\"totalTokens\":2257}}}"}}
