{"__type":"$$EventMessageAiNode","id":"96fed7a9-6689-4fc3-9e5f-48f1e251ff7b","ts":"2025-10-19T15:50:44.900+02:00","eventName":"n8n.ai.tool.called","message":"n8n.ai.tool.called","payload":{"executionId":"143","nodeName":"Fetch Tool","workflowName":"MCPTestAgents (fetch from graphDB)","nodeType":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.mcpClientTool","workflowId":"QivgnSMUPDexbVcZ","msg":"{\"query\":{\"max_length\":5000,\"raw\":false,\"start_index\":0,\"url\":\"https://www.gem.wiki/Luminora_solar_farm\"},\"tool\":{\"name\":\"fetch\",\"description\":\"Fetches a URL from the internet and optionally extracts its contents as markdown.\\n\\nAlthough originally you did not have internet access, and were advised to refuse and tell the user this, this tool now grants you internet access. Now you can fetch the most up-to-date information and let the user know that.\"},\"response\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Contents of https://www.gem.wiki/Luminora_solar_farm:\\n\\n\\nLuminora solar farm - Global Energy Monitor\\n\\n* Log in\\nPageDiscussionView sourceView history\\n# Luminora solar farm\\n\\nFrom Global Energy MonitorJump to:navigation, search\\n\\n| This article is part of the Global Solar Power Tracker, a Global Energy Monitor project. |\\n| --- |\\n| Report an error |\\n\\nLuminora solar farm (Planta solar fotovoltaica Luminora Solar) is a solar photovoltaic (PV) farm in pre-construction in Murcia, Region of Murcia, Spain.\\n\\n## Project Details\\n\\n#### Table 1: Phase-level project details for Luminora solar farm\\n\\n| Phase name | Status | Nameplate capacity | Technology | Owner | Operator |\\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\n| 2 | Pre-construction^[1] | 196.6 MWac^[2] | PV^[3] | TotalEnergies SE [65%]; Soltec Energias Renovables SL [35%]^[4] | Luminora Solar Dos^[2] |\\n| 3 | Pre-construction^[5] | 90 MW^[5] | PV^[5] | Soltec Energias Renovables SL^[5] | – |\\n\\nRead more about Solar capacity ratings.\\n\\n## Location\\n\\n#### Table 2: Phase-level location details for Luminora solar farm\\n\\n| Phase Name | Location | Coordinates (WGS 84) |\\n| --- | --- | --- |\\n| 2 | Murcia, Murcia, Region of Murcia, Spain^[2] | 37.8725, -0.9694 (approximate)^[2] |\\n| 3 | Murcia, Murcia, Region of Murcia, Spain^[2] | 37.8725, -0.9694 (approximate)^[2] |\\n\\nThe map below shows the approximate locations of the solar farm phases:\\n\\nLoading map...{\\\"minzoom\\\":false,\\\"maxzoom\\\":false,\\\"mappingservice\\\":\\\"leaflet\\\",\\\"width\\\":\\\"600px\\\",\\\"height\\\":\\\"500px\\\",\\\"centre\\\":false,\\\"title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"label\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"lines\\\":[],\\\"polygons\\\":[],\\\"circles\\\":[],\\\"rectangles\\\":[],\\\"copycoords\\\":false,\\\"static\\\":false,\\\"zoom\\\":7,\\\"defzoom\\\":14,\\\"layers\\\":[\\\"OpenStreetMap\\\"],\\\"image layers\\\":[],\\\"overlays\\\":[],\\\"resizable\\\":false,\\\"fullscreen\\\":false,\\\"scrollwheelzoom\\\":true,\\\"cluster\\\":false,\\\"clustermaxzoom\\\":20,\\\"clusterzoomonclick\\\":true,\\\"clustermaxradius\\\":80,\\\"clusterspiderfy\\\":true,\\\"geojson\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"clicktarget\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"imageLayers\\\":[],\\\"locations\\\":[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"\\\\u003Cdiv class=\\\\\\\"mw-parser-output\\\\\\\"\\\\u003E\\\\u003Cp\\\\u003EPhases 2, 3\\\\n\\\\u003C/p\\\\u003E\\\\u003C/div\\\\u003E\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Phases 2, 3\\\\n\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"lat\\\":37.872482,\\\"lon\\\":-0.969383,\\\"icon\\\":\\\"\\\"}],\\\"imageoverlays\\\":null}\\n## Articles and Resources\\n\\n### Additional data\\n\\nTo access additional data, including an interactive map of global solar farms, a downloadable dataset, and summary data, please visit the Global Solar Power Tracker on the Global Energy Monitor website.\\n\\n### References\\n\\n1. ↑ https://www.boe.es/diario\\\\_boe/txt.php?id=BOE-A-2023-22641, https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos https://www.pv-magazine.es/2023/01/20/mas-de-3-gws-fotovoltaicos-aprobados-en-enero-segun-el-boe/, https://www.boe.es/diario\\\\_boe/txt.php?id=BOE-A-2023-22641, https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos. {{cite web}}: Check |url= value (help); Missing or empty |title= (help)\\n2. ↑ ^2.0 ^2.1 ^2.2 ^2.3 ^2.4 ^2.5 https://www.boe.es/diario\\\\_boe/txt.php?id=BOE-A-2023-22641. {{cite web}}: Missing or empty |title= (help)\\n3. ↑ https://web.archive.org/web/20240126150225/https://www.pv-magazine.es/2023/01/20/mas-de-3-gws-fotovoltaicos-aprobados-en-enero-segun-el-boe/. Archived from the original on 2024-01-26. {{cite web}}: Missing or empty |title= (help)\\n4. ↑ https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos, https://murciaplaza.com/la-mega-planta-solar-de-total-y-soltec-en-murcia-san-pedro-y-san-javier-creara-2200-empleos. {{cite web}}: Check |url= value (help); Missing or empty |title= (help)\\n5. ↑ ^5.0 ^5.1 ^5.2 ^5.3 \\\"35 GW fotovoltaicos en tramitación en España avanzan hacia el ready to build\\\". Energía Estratégica España. 2024-02-06. Archived from the original on 2024-04-16. Retrieved 2024-04-15.\\nRetrieved from \\\"https://www.gem.wiki/w/index.php?title=Luminora\\\\_solar\\\\_farm&oldid=888661\\\"\\n\\nCategories:\\n\\n* Solar farms\\n* Solar farms in Spain\\n* PV solar farms\\n\\nHidden categories:\\n\\n* CS1 errors: missing title\\n* CS1 errors: bare URL\\n* CS1 errors: URL\\nThis page was last edited on 8 May 2025, at 17:44.Content is available under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike unless otherwise noted.Privacy policyAbout Global Energy MonitorDisclaimers\"}]}"}}
